</header><main><article class="section page-hero"><p class="eyebrow">College ERP guide</p><h1>Best ERP for colleges in India</h1><p class="lead">The best college ERP should support student management, attendance tracking, fee and finance, exams, reports and admissions CRM from one system.</p><p>Indian colleges need ERP software that fits local workflows: course and batch structures, fee installments, admissions follow-ups, exam results and management reporting. A good ERP should reduce manual registers and spreadsheets while giving every department accurate data.</p><h2>What to check before buying</h2><ul class="check-list"><li>Student lifecycle and document management</li><li>Attendance by course, batch and date</li><li>Fee collections, dues, receipts and finance reports</li><li>Admissions inquiry tracking and follow-ups</li><li>Role-based access for admin, staff and management</li></ul><p>CampusEdgePro - Smart College ERP by Sortiq Solutions is positioned for institutes that want a practical, connected college ERP with implementation support.</p><a class="button" href="../demo.html">Book Demo</a></article></main><script src="/assets/main.js"></script></body></html>


